#Utility for matching of rate plans between integRate and Infranet
#databases.
#
#pin_validate_rate_plans utility takes a list of [Rate_plan, Service_type] 
#tuples as input, from a text file which is generated by running an SQL script 
#(serviceTypeReport.sql in /tools/ServiceTypeReport directory in an 
#Integrate installation) which accesses the integRate database. Then it 
#compares this list with what is available in the Infranet database. 
#It generates a report containing a list of rate plans not available 
#in integRate.
#
#Each line contains one tuple with two string values. The first string
#is the rate plan name and the second one is the corresponding service
#type. The values are separated by tabs.
#
#Rate_plan_name	Service_type

Business	/service/gsm/telephony
